    "The plant breeding community can enhance the evaluation and maximization of the impact of LLMs, by measuring their performances through objective metrics such as precision, recall and accuracy and by measuring against real world datasets.",
    "This not only helps verify that LLMs can provide practical benefits over existing approaches, but also provides insights for how best to improve their use in future applications, thereby further grounding them as drivers of innovation in plant breeding.",
    "How practical is to build LLMs from scratch?",
    "The emergence and evolution of LLMs over recent years have significantly advanced artificial intelligence capabilities, enabling machines to perform complex language processing tasks with great skill and accuracy (Lam et al., 2024).",
    "However, the process of developing an LLM from the scratch involves substantial financial and computational investments."
